# Gym Website

This is a React-based gym website built with Vite.

## Project Structure

- React 18 for the UI framework
- Vite for fast development and bundling
- Modern JavaScript (ES modules)

## Development Commands

- `npm run dev` - Start the development server (already running at http://localhost:5173)
- `npm run build` - Build for production
- `npm run preview` - Preview the production build

## Getting Started

The development server is already running. Open http://localhost:5173 in your browser to view the application.
